ohue pete february   exmta chairman joseph lhota grants retroactive payraises and payouts worth  to  top agency presidents and former exec daily news new york retrieved august     a b flegenheimer matt november   free subway shuttle starting for part of rockaway peninsula the new york times   veronique hakim named interim mta executive director retrieved february     nationwide search for new head of mta starts as chairman retires retrieved february     mta  news  governor cuomo announces veronique hakim will serve as interim executive director of the mta retrieved february     lovett kenneth donohue pete katz celeste otis ginger adams december   joe lhota in possible push in mayoral race to resign as mta chairman daily news new york retrieved august     peltz jennifer exmta chief lhota files papers for mayoral run archived from the original on february   retrieved february     for new york mayor the new york times august     orden erica september   lhota wins republican primary for mayor the wall street journal   joe lhota for mayor  boiling down the two mayoral candidates to their basic experience and skill makes our choice clear crains new york business october     new york city news latest headlines videos  pictures retrieved february     elect joe lhota mayor of new york newsday october     jv staff october   vote for the most qualified candidates on november  the jewish voice endorses the following jewish voice new york ny   joe lhota for new york city mayor new york post november     republican mayoral candidate joe lhota vows to cut taxes on business properties and hotel stays daily news new york   meriwether kristen september   joe lhota’s jobs plan heavy on tax reduction epoch times   lee kristen a july   chat with nyc mayoral candidate joe lhota daily news new york   httpwwwnycomcontentnewseducationcharterschoolsupportersmarchacrossbrooklynbridge  fermino jennifer karni annie siemaszko corky november   bill de blasio elected mayor of new york city new yor